&lt;p&gt;Wealth isn&amp;rsquo;t about taking something from somebody else&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Naval:&lt;/strong&gt;
I think there is this notion that making money is evil, right? It&amp;rsquo;s rooted all the way back down to &amp;ldquo;money is the root of all evil.&amp;rdquo; People think that the bankers steal our money. It&amp;rsquo;s somewhat true in that, in a lot of the world, there&amp;rsquo;s a lot of theft going on all the time.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Make Wealth</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/wealth/</link><pubDate>Sat, 01 May 2004 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/wealth/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/wealth/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
